### **.gitignore**
Add the following entries to ignore files and directories not needed in your repository:

# Ignore node_modules if used
node_modules/

# Ignore build or distribution files
dist/
build/

# Ignore temporary or system files
*.log
*.tmp
*.swp
*.bak
*.orig
*.lock
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Ignore example artifacts
examples/*.html
examples/*.pdf

# Ignore environment or sensitive files
.env
*.env.local
.env.development
.env.production

# Ignore IDE specific files
.idea/
.vscode/
*.code-workspace
